 into this category.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p><strong>Academic and educational:<\/strong> Focuses on research and educational material. Academic research journals and syllabus-oriented textbooks fall into this category.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p><strong>Independent and regional:<\/strong> Made up of small presses focusing predominantly on materials of local or regional interest, such as local histories and tourism pamphlets.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p><strong>Boutique:<\/strong> Specializes in narrow, niche markets. Small presses publishing genre-specific fiction fall into this category, for example.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p><strong>Self-publishing:<\/strong> The creator of the material pays the publishing costs and plays a much bigger role in the process.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p><strong>Electronic:<\/strong> Offers an alternative to traditional publishing, sharing content across digital platforms only.<\/p>\n"}]}]},{"@type":"HowToSection","position":"2","name":"<p>Name your business.<\/p>\n","itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"1","name":"<p>Come up with a name.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Give your company a name. There are a number of things to consider when naming your publishing company to successfully convey the values and mission of your brand, but you'll want to be creative. A unique name will set your company apart from the rest and will make it easier later when securing a domain name.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-publishing-company#how-to-start-a-publishing-company-section2-step1","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-how-to-start-a-publishing-company-name-288x288-20200811.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p><strong>Think specifics:<\/strong> What genre are you working in? What subject, and for what age groups?<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p><strong>Revisit values:<\/strong> What are your business's core values? And what values does your market hold as important?<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>Your name should be easy to remember, spell, and say.<\/p>\n"}]},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"2","name":"<p>Check availability.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Use the U.S. Patent and Trademark Office\u2019s <a href=\"https:\/\/www.uspto.gov\/trademarks\">trademark search tool<\/a> to see if your name isn't already in use.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-publishing-company#how-to-start-a-publishing-company-section2-step2","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-how-to-start-a-publishing-company-check-288x288-20200813.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>Follow this guide on <a href=\"https:\/\/www.namesnack.com\/guides\/how-to-check-if-a-business-name-is-available-for-free\">How to Check Business Name Availability<\/a> for a more thorough check.<\/p>\n"}]},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"3","name":"<p>Trademark your business name.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>If you have decided on a publishing company business name, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.namesnack.com\/guides\/how-to-trademark-a-name\">secure a trademark<\/a> so that no one else takes it. You can register a trademark at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.uspto.gov\/\">www.uspto.gov<\/a>.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-publishing-company#how-to-start-a-publishing-company-section2-step3","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-how-to-start-a-publishing-company-trademark-288x288-20200813.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToDirection","text":"<p>Go to the U.S. Patent and Trademark Office <a href=\"https:\/\/www.uspto.gov\/\">website<\/a>.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToDir