ditional-288x288-20200811.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>While this model does allow for bulk printing and <strong>ensures consistently good quality<\/strong>, it is <strong>expensive upfront<\/strong> because it carries storage, returns, and shipping fees.<\/p>\n"}]},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"3","name":"<p>Consider the direct-to-reader model.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Consider whether cutting out most of the distribution chain and selling digital publications directly to readers through an online sales page makes sense for your company.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-publishing-company#how-to-start-a-publishing-company-section3-step3","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-how-to-start-a-publishing-company-dtr-288x288-20200811.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>There are <strong>very little upfront costs and risks<\/strong> with this model, but a comprehensive <strong>marketing strategy is needed<\/strong>.<\/p>\n"}]}]},{"@type":"HowToSection","position":"4","name":"<p>Create a publishing company business plan.<\/p>\n","itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"1","name":"<p>Write the business description section.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Leave a page for the executive summary, which should be written last, and start with the business description section. This section includes legal structure, location, the expected launch dates of publications, and all sources of revenue.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-publishing-company#how-to-start-a-publishing-company-section4-step1","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-how-to-start-a-publishing-company-description-288x288-20200812.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"2","n